The Tesla Wall Connector is the obvious choice if you want everything to stay within the Tesla ecosystem. It integrates natively with the Tesla app, so you can monitor charging, set schedules, and track energy usage all in one place.

On a standard UK single-phase supply, it delivers **7.4kW** — exactly the same as every other charger on this list. If you happen to have three-phase power (rare in UK homes, but some do), it can push up to **22kW**, which is a genuine advantage.

